REACTION   (61-PM-147(N,G)61-PM-148,,SIG)
SAMPLE      U-235 fission product
DECAY-DATA (61-PM-147,2.6YR)
ANALYSIS   Pm-147 neutron absorption cross-section was determined
           by dividing equation (1) from equation (2) by measured
           fission yields of Pm-147 and Nd-146, their decay
           constants, irradiation and cooling times.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Type of uncertainty is not explained in the
            article.
