BIB                  6         12
REACTION   (62-SM-147(N,G)62-SM-148,,SIG)
SAMPLE      U-235 fission product
ANALYSIS   Sm-147 absorption cross section was determined by
           solving equation (3) simultaneously with other
           equations, analogous (1) and (2), using the measured
           fission yields of Pm-147 and Sm-147, their decay
           constants, irradiation and cooling times.
